lead_paragraph: British Member of Parliament Damian Collins used parliamentary privilege on Tuesday to accuse FIFA presidential candidate Sheikh Salman Bin Ebrahim Al Khalifa of taking development project funds to finance an election bid.

headline.print_headline: FIFA Candidate Salman Denies British MP's Allegations
